ygData.messageBody: The other nite I killed a skeleton or maybe a necros pet in S. Karanas and recieved a "Rat Shaped Ring" off of it. Now in Qeynos at the Cleric guild one of the Npc's said to bring these back to them does anyone know what I get for turning it in cause if its not good enough then Ill keep it cus its +10 to poison and disease:) anyone know what that will sale for also?
